<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 30 at 4:53AM EST  by NWS Albany</headline>
<description>...Patchy dense fog through the morning commute...
Patchy dense fog continues over portions of eastern New York and
western New England this morning. Visibility of less than half a
mile is expected in some spots. Motorists should allow extra time
to get to their destinations this morning and leave plenty of room
between vehicles.</description>
